{
  "texts": [
    "We formulate a novel research problem: detecting evolving LLM-generated disinformation.",
    "We proposed DELD, a simple and efficient method that effectively leverages the fact-checking capabilities of pre-trained language models and integrates the unique disinformation characteristics of various LLMs.",
    "Our extensive experiments demonstrate that DELD significantly outperforms existing methods, achieving superior performance in detecting evolving disinformation generated(a) Human-written.",
    "(b) Vicuna.",
    "(d) ChatGPT."
  ]
}